# Top-level files
# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.
.vscode/

# API
## Environments
/api/.venv/
/api/venv/
/api/env/

## Environment Variables (Secrets!)
/api/.env

## Python Cache
/api/__pycache__/
/api/*.pyc

## Mac System Files
/api/.DS_Store

# Web

## dependencies
/web/node_modules
/web/.pnp
/web/.pnp.*
/web/.yarn/*
/web/!.yarn/patches
/web/!.yarn/plugins
/web/!.yarn/releases
/web/!.yarn/versions

## testing
/web/coverage

## next.js
/web/.next/
/web/out/

## production
/web/build

## misc
/web/.DS_Store
/web/*.pem

## debug
/web/npm-debug.log*
/web/yarn-debug.log*
/web/yarn-error.log*
/web/.pnpm-debug.log*

## env files (can opt-in for committing if needed)
/web/.env*

## vercel
/web/.vercel

## typescript
/web/*.tsbuildinfo
/web/next-env.d.ts

## Editor directories and files
/web/.vscode/
